00:00:11,533 --> 00:00:20,291
<i>Maiko Monogatari (1954)</i>

3
00:01:32,898 --> 00:01:39,523
A train departing from Tokyo is currently arriving at platform 4.

4
00:01:46,047 --> 00:01:48,633
Kyoto.Kyoto.

5
00:01:54,039 --> 00:01:55,898
Arrived in Kyoto

6
00:01:56,530 --> 00:01:59,874
You can transfer here

7
00:02:00,944 --> 00:02:02,384
Thank you very much.

8
00:02:02,409 --> 00:02:03,789
Take care.

9
00:02:04,766 --> 00:02:05,781
See you.

10
00:02:07,555 --> 00:02:08,750
Oh Tome!

11
00:02:09,242 --> 00:02:10,209
Over here!

12
00:02:11,328 --> 00:02:12,992
Thank you for coming early.

13
00:02:13,017 --> 00:02:14,937
I think you're tired after a long train ride.

14
00:02:15,810 --> 00:02:16,773
How is your mother?

15
00:02:16,798 --> 00:02:19,828
I hope she's doing well.
Let's go to the hospital together.

16
00:02:21,805 --> 00:02:23,961
Eiji.
Welcome back.

17
00:02:25,180 --> 00:02:27,141
Is she someone you know?

18
00:02:27,861 --> 00:02:29,961
She was next to me.

19
00:02:31,164 --> 00:02:33,243
Will you come to my house tonight?

20
00:02:33,760 --> 00:02:35,039
It's my birthday.

21
00:02:35,071 --> 00:02:36,860
I forgot about that.

22
00:03:07,274 --> 00:03:09,774
Mom.

23
00:03:11,874 --> 00:03:17,937
I'm glad you came back.
You didn't have to force yourself to come back.

24
00:03:18,910 --> 00:03:26,562
I can't concentrate on studying until I see how mom is doing for a minute

25
00:03:26,587 --> 00:03:30,062
that's true. You don't have to worry because you're well-off

26
00:03:30,560 --> 00:03:35,586
I told her not to worry and that she could come.

27
00:03:36,555 --> 00:03:38,250
I'm sorry for making you worry.

28
00:03:39,151 --> 00:03:46,331
What are you saying? It's better for you to have her by your side

29
00:03:46,880 --> 00:03:49,851
I've been taking care of you.

30
00:03:50,039 --> 00:03:52,055
What is your temperature today?

31
00:03:56,183 --> 00:03:57,734
It seems good.

32
00:03:58,008 --> 00:04:00,821
so please take care of yourself

33
00:04:00,914 --> 00:04:01,993
Thank you very much.

34
00:04:02,258 --> 00:04:06,211
Our work is lonely without you.

35
00:04:07,368 --> 00:04:09,313
I'm not that important.

36
00:04:09,434 --> 00:04:11,500
Really.

37
00:04:12,586 --> 00:04:16,274
Will you return with me?

38
00:04:16,664 --> 00:04:18,765
I'm going to stay right here by my mother's side

39
00:04:18,836 --> 00:04:21,008
You're good.

40
00:04:21,524 --> 00:04:24,571
Please do that.
You are the only two parents.

41
00:04:25,055 --> 00:04:30,538
I have a party today.
Take care.

42
00:04:32,125 --> 00:04:34,078
I'll be here again.

43
00:04:34,586 --> 00:04:36,032
Please look after her.

44
00:04:36,391 --> 00:04:37,750
See you.

45
00:04:40,008 --> 00:04:41,625
Take care.

46
00:04:47,035 --> 00:04:50,035
How about your condition?

47
00:04:51,368 --> 00:04:52,961
Are you okay if you don't go to school?

48
00:04:53,139 --> 00:04:57,023
It's ok.Even if I take a little break, I'll show you that I can make up for it quickly.

49
00:04:57,282 --> 00:04:58,438
I'm smart.

50
00:05:02,419 --> 00:05:06,836
What are you planning to do if you graduate?

51
00:05:08,304 --> 00:05:11,711
I want to go back to Kyoto and do clinical work at my father's hospital

52
00:05:12,050 --> 00:05:15,050
I think your father would be pleased with that.

53
00:05:17,625 --> 00:05:26,220
You two should take your time and enjoy your conversation.

54
00:05:26,930 --> 00:05:29,008
Thank you.

55
00:05:29,164 --> 00:05:30,633
Are there any other customers here?

56
00:05:30,658 --> 00:05:33,789
Yoko left it just the two of us.
let's start.

57
00:05:55,798 --> 00:05:57,203
Happy birthday!

58
00:05:58,485 --> 00:05:59,625
Congratulations!

59
00:05:59,773 --> 00:06:00,671
Thank you

60
00:06:01,831 --> 00:06:04,265
Welcome back!

61
00:06:04,290 --> 00:06:08,711
Sorry for being so late, it's been a while

62
00:06:12,791 --> 00:06:14,317
Dad, congratulations

63
00:06:14,380 --> 00:06:17,380
Brother, today is my birthday.

64
00:06:17,547 --> 00:06:18,961
Sorry.

65
00:06:19,118 --> 00:06:20,243
Congratulations!

66
00:06:20,352 --> 00:06:21,782
It's like you're married.

67
00:06:22,156 --> 00:06:23,117
It's kind of that.

68
00:06:30,089 --> 00:06:36,883
Since I saw your face and instantly I became lively again

69
00:06:37,694 --> 00:06:41,765
Don't worry about me. I'll be back in Tokyo in a few days.

70
00:06:43,274 --> 00:06:43,836
I will do that.

71
00:06:45,015 --> 00:06:47,215
but your is so energetic

72
00:06:47,240 --> 00:06:47,984
I feel relieved

73
00:06:49,140 --> 00:06:52,953
But since I've finally come back, I'll do my best to look after you.

74
00:06:59,300 --> 00:07:03,586
That's silly, there's no need to take that seriously, is there?

75
00:07:05,157 --> 00:07:07,305
Please eat that meal quickly.

76
00:07:09,309 --> 00:07:11,499
Have a eat.

77
00:07:12,087 --> 00:07:16,804
I've been on the train all this time so my stomach's not feeling well.

78
00:07:17,090 --> 00:07:18,234
That's bad.

79
00:07:19,000 --> 00:07:20,695
So, what happened?

80
00:07:21,899 --> 00:07:23,750
Well.

81
00:07:40,664 --> 00:07:41,547
Is there something wrong?

82
00:07:46,336 --> 00:07:48,336
You look like you're in pain

83
00:07:48,657 --> 00:07:49,391
Yes.

84
00:07:50,414 --> 00:07:52,657
Do you have a stomach ache?

85
00:07:59,731 --> 00:08:02,731
I'll bring you some water now.
Please eat this.

86
00:08:02,844 --> 00:08:03,641
Sorry about that.

87
00:08:20,266 --> 00:08:21,430
Thank you very much.

88
00:08:25,305 --> 00:08:27,125
Please take a rest.

89
00:08:29,945 --> 00:08:32,055
You should lie down since the medicine is still working

90
00:08:32,080 --> 00:08:33,668
But....

91
00:08:34,379 --> 00:08:36,937
I'm still a medical student, so of course I'm taking care of you.

92
00:08:37,016 --> 00:08:37,461
But.

93
00:08:37,486 --> 00:08:38,844
Follow my advice

94
00:08:39,698 --> 00:08:40,523
I'm sorry.

95
00:08:42,299 --> 00:08:48,990
You received a very honest response from him, but you never heard his name.

96
00:08:51,616 --> 00:08:54,250
What were you doing?

97
00:08:55,421 --> 00:08:57,515
You can't repay him

98
00:08:58,900 --> 00:09:02,298
I was embarrassed to hear his name.

99
00:09:03,409 --> 00:09:07,305
There's no need to be embarrassed to say thank him

100
00:09:08,337 --> 00:09:11,563
You are too shy.

101
00:09:19,610 --> 00:09:22,415
When did you come back?

102
00:09:22,440 --> 00:09:24,250
I came back last night on the night train.

103
00:09:24,343 --> 00:09:26,602
Did you see your mom?

104
00:09:26,868 --> 00:09:29,501
I think you were surprised.

105
00:09:30,673 --> 00:09:32,181
Have you been here for a while?

106
00:09:32,865 --> 00:09:35,865
Take good care of your mom.

107
00:09:36,242 --> 00:09:37,547
Thank you very much.

108
00:09:43,001 --> 00:09:43,907
What's wrong?

109
00:09:45,251 --> 00:09:46,884
Come in.

110
00:09:54,681 --> 00:09:56,063
How was her?

111
00:09:57,100 --> 00:10:00,100
She look fine.
Is her illness serious?

112
00:10:01,092 --> 00:10:06,196
According to the doctor, there are a lot of bad things with her body.

113
00:10:07,225 --> 00:10:12,157
so what are you going to do about it? The hospital costs are ridiculous,

114
00:10:13,359 --> 00:10:16,000
and until now, your aunt has been helping out

115
00:10:16,345 --> 00:10:18,212
Sorry for the inconvenience.

116
00:10:19,973 --> 00:10:25,102
If I'm fine, my job is fine.

117
00:10:26,024 --> 00:10:29,391
I think it'll be okay without your mother.

118
00:10:30,850 --> 00:10:32,316
Even if I want to help somehow,

119
00:10:32,340 --> 00:10:34,290
Last night I thought about various things.

120
00:10:35,455 --> 00:10:37,213
About the house

121
00:10:37,923 --> 00:10:40,923
If your mother is hospitalized for a long time

122
00:10:41,501 --> 00:10:46,087
How about cutting back on that economy?
How about firing the maid?

123
00:10:47,647 --> 00:10:51,314
I don't think it's worth the money to pay them.

124
00:10:55,888 --> 00:10:59,228
I was against you going to school in Tokyo.

125
00:10:59,860 --> 00:11:05,626
Your Mom understood, but think about it—like mother, like child;

126
00:11:06,260 --> 00:11:08,196
If you were a Maiko,

127
00:11:08,330 --> 00:11:10,861
I'd take care of you

128
00:11:11,578 --> 00:11:13,712
Think about that.

129
00:11:14,353 --> 00:11:17,360
I can say that this obi suits that kimono.

130
00:11:18,008 --> 00:11:23,360
If you say something like that,I sing like this

131
00:11:27,861 --> 00:11:29,658
My throat hurts.

132
00:11:29,683 --> 00:11:31,736
Is someone making a strange noise?

133
00:11:33,111 --> 00:11:35,213
I felt bad.

134
00:11:35,353 --> 00:11:36,346
Why you're here?

135
00:11:36,533 --> 00:11:37,908
I'm here to pay my bill.

136
00:11:38,424 --> 00:11:40,634
Thank you very much.

137
00:11:40,955 --> 00:11:41,736
Have a seat.

138
00:11:41,761 --> 00:11:42,955
I'm leaving.

139
00:11:43,049 --> 00:11:44,713
Think about that.

140
00:11:47,002 --> 00:11:48,080
Please.

141
00:11:52,924 --> 00:11:53,689
Who's her?

142
00:11:54,033 --> 00:11:55,611
Satogiku's daughter.

143
00:11:57,298 --> 00:12:00,298
Isn't she a nice girl?

144
00:12:08,041 --> 00:12:08,900
Is she your sister?

145
00:12:09,596 --> 00:12:11,564
She's my daughter.

146
00:12:13,368 --> 00:12:16,368
I didn't know there was such a big daughter.

147
00:12:27,072 --> 00:12:28,049
Take care.

148
00:12:44,446 --> 00:12:46,455
Mom.

149
00:12:49,471 --> 00:12:50,674
I see.

150
00:12:58,758 --> 00:13:02,145
Why did they let her get this bad?

151
00:13:02,170 --> 00:13:06,056
People in that kind of society tend to push themselves without realizing it

152
00:13:06,261 --> 00:13:07,414
Does she have cirrhosis?

153
00:13:08,126 --> 00:13:10,876
That's a possibility, so we're taking x-rays to investigate.

154
00:13:11,917 --> 00:13:12,767
If it's a cancer?.

155
00:13:12,846 --> 00:13:14,510
there's no hope at all.

156
00:13:16,400 --> 00:13:17,494
Her daughter knows that?

157
00:13:17,846 --> 00:13:18,939
Nobody knows about it yet.

158
00:13:35,790 --> 00:13:36,985
How're you?

159
00:13:37,198 --> 00:13:40,033
Thank you very much.

160
00:13:40,697 --> 00:13:45,267
You took care of my daughter on the train.

161
00:13:47,182 --> 00:13:49,432
I want to thank you a lot.

162
00:13:50,135 --> 00:13:54,455
She's out right now but will be back soon.

163
00:13:55,344 --> 00:14:01,463
She received your kind help.
But she didn't ask your name. Sorry.

164
00:14:01,736 --> 00:14:03,096
Don't worry.

165
00:14:04,627 --> 00:14:05,908
Please.

166
00:14:19,728 --> 00:14:21,400
I apologize for that earlier.

167
00:14:21,425 --> 00:14:23,923
My mother said she wanted to meet you and express her gratitude

168
00:14:23,948 --> 00:14:25,041
I just visited her.

169
00:14:25,143 --> 00:14:26,283
Oh really?

170
00:14:26,415 --> 00:14:29,155
She was so politely thanked that I ended up feeling troubled.

171
00:14:50,355 --> 00:14:53,355
How is my mother's condition?

172
00:14:57,329 --> 00:14:59,689
I don't really understand well

173
00:14:59,841 --> 00:15:01,314
but I don't think there's anything to worry about

174
00:15:01,377 --> 00:15:02,619
I see.

175
00:15:03,588 --> 00:15:08,510
I was relieved to hear that.

176
00:15:14,987 --> 00:15:16,712
What a nice mother she is

177
00:15:20,459 --> 00:15:23,459
How long will you be staying in Kyoto?

178
00:15:24,877 --> 00:15:26,205
I have school

179
00:15:26,757 --> 00:15:28,181
so I can't stay for too long

180
00:15:30,236 --> 00:15:32,064
You want to go to music college, right?

181
00:15:32,089 --> 00:15:36,494
Did my mother even tell you about that?

182
00:15:39,093 --> 00:15:42,610
but I might have to give up on that now

183
00:15:43,100 --> 00:15:43,838
Why?

184
00:15:51,547 --> 00:15:53,785
Are you just your mother and your family?

185
00:16:00,471 --> 00:16:01,494
Don't worry.

186
00:16:07,009 --> 00:16:09,945
I don't really understand much about music

187
00:16:09,970 --> 00:16:12,533
The other day in Tokyo, I was so moved to watch a concert.

188
00:16:12,603 --> 00:16:13,830
It was amazing.

189
00:16:13,862 --> 00:16:14,900
Were you there too?

190
00:16:14,925 --> 00:16:16,411
We might meet.

191
00:16:16,580 --> 00:16:17,416
I was on the third floor.

192
00:16:17,775 --> 00:16:18,736
Me too.

193
00:16:18,776 --> 00:16:19,646
but speaking of which

194
00:16:20,152 --> 00:16:23,939
There was a female student next to me who sighed at that time.
Was she you?

195
00:16:24,166 --> 00:16:25,182
Really?

196
00:16:26,586 --> 00:16:31,283
The man next to me at the time was snoring the whole time.

197
00:16:31,471 --> 00:16:32,666
I remember it well.

198
00:16:32,737 --> 00:16:35,611
Well, he might have been me.

199
00:16:54,939 --> 00:16:58,197
Will my illness get better?

200
00:16:58,836 --> 00:17:01,102
I'll do my best with what I can,

201
00:17:01,350 --> 00:17:03,304
but I think it's ultimately a matter of time

202
00:17:03,914 --> 00:17:05,554
What do you mean?

203
00:17:05,947 --> 00:17:08,637
It would be nice if she will alive for six months.

204
00:17:08,662 --> 00:17:12,644
I feel sorry about her.

205
00:17:20,017 --> 00:17:21,570
Is that so?

206
00:17:23,244 --> 00:17:24,291
I see.

207
00:17:25,441 --> 00:17:28,441
It's quite lively now.

208
00:17:30,340 --> 00:17:34,000
She was talking interesting.

209
00:17:35,329 --> 00:17:37,389
I came a little too late.

210
00:17:39,313 --> 00:17:41,837
Even though you are always busy,

211
00:17:41,868 --> 00:17:44,868
I'm glad you visit me.

212
00:17:44,893 --> 00:17:47,152
Your complexion has improved.

213
00:17:47,953 --> 00:17:49,173
I'm glad

214
00:17:49,828 --> 00:17:52,090
As expected, Tome is back so you get better.

215
00:17:52,411 --> 00:17:54,291
Thank you very much.

216
00:17:54,981 --> 00:17:58,776
Let me know if you need something.

217
00:17:59,074 --> 00:18:00,087
Thank you very much.

218
00:18:01,386 --> 00:18:07,668
She has really done well, so I am not inconvenienced.

219
00:18:08,370 --> 00:18:11,370
Tome,you're great.

220
00:18:12,222 --> 00:18:14,400
I'm going to buy you a reward.

221
00:18:14,611 --> 00:18:15,518
that would make me happy

222
00:18:15,648 --> 00:18:17,208
I wonder what I want.

223
00:18:17,579 --> 00:18:18,339
Tome.

224
00:18:19,713 --> 00:18:20,499
What do you want?

225
00:18:25,974 --> 00:18:27,001
Wanna have lunch?

226
00:18:27,616 --> 00:18:29,798
Let's have a lunch with me as a reward,

227
00:18:31,717 --> 00:18:34,111
I'll get ready.

228
00:18:34,485 --> 00:18:37,879
It's better to wear nice clothes.

229
00:18:38,811 --> 00:18:41,515
And get your hair done.

230
00:18:41,540 --> 00:18:41,999
Yes.

231
00:18:47,563 --> 00:18:50,563
It must look beautiful from here on the day of Daimonji

232
00:18:51,086 --> 00:18:52,920
Next time, let's take Mom to see it!

233
00:19:06,045 --> 00:19:06,611
Tome.

234
00:19:08,083 --> 00:19:10,417
What will you do if Mom's illness doesn't get better?

235
00:19:12,927 --> 00:19:17,402
According to the doctor,her liver is really bad.

236
00:19:17,861 --> 00:19:18,768
Her liver?

237
00:19:19,879 --> 00:19:20,985
Mom's cancer?

238
00:19:21,010 --> 00:19:21,872
No no.

239
00:19:22,262 --> 00:19:24,149
If she has cancer, she won't live six months.

240
00:19:24,621 --> 00:19:26,351
She'll get better?

241
00:19:27,176 --> 00:19:31,049
Even if she recover, she won't be able to go out.

242
00:19:32,952 --> 00:19:37,114
You shouldn't let your mother know about this.

243
00:19:40,860 --> 00:19:43,436
Why don't you become Maiko?

244
00:19:49,402 --> 00:19:53,545
In the end, making your mother feel at ease and emotionally supported means you have to work

245
00:19:54,110 --> 00:19:56,841
If you want to work, how about becoming a maiko?

246
00:19:57,394 --> 00:19:59,669
You're good at both singing and dancing

247
00:20:00,377 --> 00:20:02,991
Your mother was really looking forward to that

248
00:20:06,370 --> 00:20:09,146
I know you have to think about it.

249
00:20:09,863 --> 00:20:12,343
But it's okay to take your time to think about it

250
00:20:13,169 --> 00:20:14,920
Don't push yourself.

251
00:20:15,476 --> 00:20:19,241
I will come up with various ideas for you, understood?

252
00:20:20,892 --> 00:20:23,345
Wanna have a tea? No?

253
00:20:24,198 --> 00:20:25,091
Let's go.

254
00:20:35,107 --> 00:20:36,358
Thank you very much.

255
00:20:38,002 --> 00:20:39,342
Hello?

256
00:20:39,482 --> 00:20:40,649
It's been ages.

257
00:20:40,775 --> 00:20:41,527
See you.

258
00:20:41,624 --> 00:20:42,412
Who's her?

259
00:20:43,030 --> 00:20:44,349
She's Gion's tea house madam.

260
00:20:46,305 --> 00:20:47,871
I need to make a phone call.

261
00:20:56,700 --> 00:20:58,066
Hello, I'm Eiji.

262
00:20:58,616 --> 00:20:59,553
Yoko?

263
00:21:01,340 --> 00:21:02,290
I have an internship tomorrow

264
00:21:02,315 --> 00:21:03,964
I absolutely have to be in Tokyo tonight.

265
00:21:05,340 --> 00:21:07,532
I have preparations to make, so I'm going home

266
00:21:07,774 --> 00:21:10,265
Well then, please take care of Keisuke.

267
00:21:13,493 --> 00:21:14,766
From Yoko?

268
00:21:15,085 --> 00:21:15,491
Yes.

269
00:21:15,719 --> 00:21:17,054
Why did you turn down?

270
00:21:19,833 --> 00:21:21,482
She'll take me to the station tonight.

271
00:21:39,707 --> 00:21:40,652
Yes.

272
00:21:43,275 --> 00:21:44,244
How's your mom?

273
00:21:44,727 --> 00:21:46,226
Yes, Mom is sleeping right now.

274
00:21:46,746 --> 00:21:47,467
Excuse me.

