I'm counting on you.
See you then.

824
01:17:23,840 --> 01:17:26,840
Hello, Is that Takatsugi hospital?

825
01:17:26,932 --> 01:17:31,582
Is Mr. Eiji there?
This is Itami.

826
01:17:34,666 --> 01:17:37,078
I see, thank you very much.

827
01:17:57,695 --> 01:17:59,961
Hello, is that Takatsugi? Is Mr

828
01:18:00,132 --> 01:18:01,832
Is Mr. Eiji there?

829
01:18:04,688 --> 01:18:06,741
I also tried calling the hospital.

830
01:18:09,205 --> 01:18:10,567
I apologize for the inconvenience.

831
01:20:00,944 --> 01:20:03,698
Hello, yes, this is it.

832
01:20:04,510 --> 01:20:08,374
Mr Eiji? Please hold on a moment

833
01:20:22,773 --> 01:20:23,360
From who?

834
01:20:23,593 --> 01:20:25,406
She didn't say anything.

835
01:20:27,053 --> 01:20:28,770
Hello, it's me, Eiji.

836
01:20:30,460 --> 01:20:30,907
Hello?

837
01:20:36,005 --> 01:20:36,665
Hello?

838
01:20:38,609 --> 01:20:39,142
Hello?

839
01:20:40,919 --> 01:20:41,459
Hello?

840
01:20:55,043 --> 01:20:57,454
Satogiku has come.

841
01:20:57,479 --> 01:20:58,483
I see.

842
01:21:01,605 --> 01:21:02,851
Tome.

843
01:21:04,130 --> 01:21:07,823
Thanks for coming.
Fukudome is waiting for you.

844
01:21:08,627 --> 01:21:10,107
I'll have one drink.

845
01:21:10,404 --> 01:21:12,384
Come in.

846
01:21:32,895 --> 01:21:34,162
What's wrong?

847
01:21:36,281 --> 01:21:37,561
Can you drink?

848
01:21:38,281 --> 01:21:39,207
Just little.

849
01:21:44,801 --> 01:21:46,809
Are you alright?

850
01:22:01,570 --> 01:22:03,564
I'll let you know as soon as she's ready

851
01:22:03,589 --> 01:22:04,718
Thanks.

852
01:22:10,343 --> 01:22:13,355
Let's go together with him tomorrow morning

853
01:22:14,330 --> 01:22:16,513
I am also going along with you.

854
01:22:19,390 --> 01:22:22,390
Please come in.

855
01:22:23,820 --> 01:22:25,514
Are you ready?

856
01:22:26,717 --> 01:22:28,064
I'm counting on you.

857
01:22:31,442 --> 01:22:32,669
Wanna change clothes?

858
01:22:33,142 --> 01:22:34,149
I'll help it myself.

859
01:22:48,903 --> 01:22:50,428
Sorry for making you wait.

860
01:22:53,951 --> 01:22:56,691
She's all set.

861
01:22:57,360 --> 01:23:00,360
President, please relax.

862
01:23:01,107 --> 01:23:02,773
You are stupid.

863
01:23:10,833 --> 01:23:11,880
Excuse me.

864
01:23:14,842 --> 01:23:16,609
She's still child.

865
01:23:17,184 --> 01:23:19,264
Please look after her.

866
01:23:21,616 --> 01:23:22,623
I know.

867
01:23:24,018 --> 01:23:25,271
I'm counting on you.

868
01:24:10,025 --> 01:24:12,199
Shall we wake up a little and talk?

869
01:24:16,764 --> 01:24:17,824
Satogiku

870
01:24:19,019 --> 01:24:21,052
How's it going? Have you already gone to sleep?

871
01:24:22,642 --> 01:24:26,836
You sleep with your kimono on.

872
01:24:28,888 --> 01:24:30,728
Take it off.

873
01:24:47,624 --> 01:24:49,964
Okami!

874
01:24:50,701 --> 01:24:51,608
Okami!

875
01:25:00,476 --> 01:25:05,700
I have always believed that there is nothing stronger than love in this world

876
01:25:06,955 --> 01:25:10,744
As long as I love, I thought I could overcome any obstacle

877
01:25:12,330 --> 01:25:15,806
But I have various burdens that I cannot bear alone

878
01:25:17,370 --> 01:25:21,885
I am sorry for making you, Eiji, chase after those burdens as well

879
01:25:23,740 --> 01:25:27,955
I have decided to pursue those burdens on my own

880
01:25:29,551 --> 01:25:31,626
After all, that was my destiny.

881
01:25:33,698 --> 01:25:37,760
I had a foolish heart with happiness I didn't want

882
01:25:38,770 --> 01:25:40,095
Laughing at myself now

883
01:25:41,238 --> 01:25:49,127
I hope you and Eiji will live a happy life together.

884
01:26:09,776 --> 01:26:10,543
I see.

885
01:26:13,119 --> 01:26:13,939
From hospital?

886
01:26:13,979 --> 01:26:14,339
Yes.

887
01:26:18,530 --> 01:26:19,666
She's saved.

888
01:26:30,110 --> 01:26:33,110
Brother, do you have a favor to ask me?

889
01:26:40,546 --> 01:26:41,885
Why didn't you consult me?

890
01:26:45,803 --> 01:26:46,669
You are stupid.

891
01:26:47,440 --> 01:26:49,855
You can do anything if you are willing to die for it.

892
01:27:00,866 --> 01:27:03,866
Don't ever do anything like that again.

893
01:27:14,821 --> 01:27:15,294
Yes.

894
01:27:19,790 --> 01:27:21,038
Is it okay if I come in?

895
01:27:21,586 --> 01:27:22,166
Yes.

896
01:27:33,462 --> 01:27:39,183
I'm glad you are saved.
I read the letter and understood your feelings

897
01:27:39,560 --> 01:27:40,788
I'm very happy.

898
01:27:43,804 --> 01:27:46,153
and I came to thank you.

899
01:27:51,539 --> 01:27:52,358
Tomeko.

900
01:27:53,689 --> 01:27:58,864
It must have been tough for you, Tomoko-san, right? But it's okay now

901
01:27:59,513 --> 01:28:02,513
Are you only thinking about Eri-san?

902
01:28:06,154 --> 01:28:07,068
But...

903
01:28:07,849 --> 01:28:09,709
Don't say anything.

904
01:28:13,015 --> 01:28:14,746
We are fair now.

905
01:28:17,610 --> 01:28:18,766
then, take care.

906
01:28:20,190 --> 01:28:21,844
I have something to talk with you,Eiji.

907
01:28:45,850 --> 01:28:48,850
I would like you to receive this, Tomoko-san,

908
01:28:49,821 --> 01:28:51,139
TOMEKO's Testimonials.

909
01:28:51,389 --> 01:28:52,369
TOMEKO's Testimonials?

910
01:28:53,844 --> 01:28:55,170
Why do you have this?

911
01:28:55,525 --> 01:28:57,465
This is present for you.

912
01:28:58,112 --> 01:29:00,005
It's troubling for me.

913
01:29:01,220 --> 01:29:01,913
Why not?

914
01:29:03,509 --> 01:29:06,509
I don't want to cause trouble for your family

915
01:29:13,256 --> 01:29:14,562
Why do you say like that?

916
01:29:16,828 --> 01:29:18,999
Why can't you just accept it quietly?

917
01:29:19,618 --> 01:29:20,738
I really understand your actions

918
01:29:22,209 --> 01:29:23,812
But that wouldn't settle my feelings

919
01:29:24,025 --> 01:29:30,539
Keep this with me until I make up my mind.

920
01:29:37,485 --> 01:29:39,846
Just take it as it comes.

921
01:29:43,707 --> 01:29:44,561
Please.

922
01:30:54,723 --> 01:30:56,308
Look, over there.

923
01:31:07,562 --> 01:31:08,889
Tome is there.

924
01:31:09,715 --> 01:31:10,549
Stop it.

925
01:31:11,372 --> 01:31:12,906
1.2.3.

926
01:31:13,230 --> 01:31:16,070
Tome-chan!

927
01:31:49,167 --> 01:31:56,867
THE END

